<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>D&uuml;w&uuml;rtigi&#328;
di&#328;e derini&#328; seboreiki &yacute;erlerinde - sebaceous bezlerini&#328;
konsentrasi&yacute;a &yacute;erinde lokalla&#351;&yacute;an
g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;i.&nbsp;Bular kell&auml;ni&#328;, nasolabial we
gulagy&#328; eplen&yacute;&auml;n &yacute;erlerini&#328;,
d&ouml;&#351;&uuml;ni&#328; we kesi&#351;&yacute;&auml;n
sebtidir.&nbsp;A&yacute;ratynlyk&nbsp;<b>&quot;psoriatik
t&auml;&ccedil;&quot;&nbsp;</b>- kell&auml;ni&#328; derisinden
ma&#328;la&yacute;yna ge&ccedil;megi bilen kell&auml;&#328;ize ulal&yacute;an
ulalmak bilen d&ouml;k&uuml;lm&auml;ni&#328; belli bir nag&#351;y emele
gel&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

