14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Keseli&#328; &yacute;iti
g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;i.&nbsp;&#350;ol bir wagty&#328; &ouml;z&uuml;nde, az
