</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>&Ccedil;ilimi ta&#351;lamak we alkogol i&ccedil;gileri
toshba&yacute;az keselini&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>erbetle&#351;dir&yacute;&auml;n
belli faktorlardyr.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Dermanlar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Da&#351;arky bejergi</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>M&ouml;h&uuml;m gl&yacute;ukokortikosteroidler&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&yacute;erli
gormonal seri&#351;deler bolup, islendik g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;de
kombinasi&yacute;a &yacute;a-da monoterapi&yacute;a g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;inde
ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Bu dermanlary ulanmagy&#328; a&yacute;ratyn
d&uuml;zg&uuml;nleri bar: esasanam &ccedil;agalarda gow&#351;ak &yacute;a-da
orta i&#351;je&#328;ligi&#328; gl&yacute;ukokortikosteroidlerinden ba&#351;lap
kursy dolandyrmak.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>D3 witaminini&#328; analoglaryny &ouml;z i&ccedil;ine al&yacute;an
ta&yacute;&yacute;arlyklar&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>- bu
ta&yacute;&yacute;arlyklary&#328; ulanyl&yacute;an &yacute;eri bedeni&#328;
&uuml;st&uuml;nd&auml;ki 30% -den k&ouml;p bolmaly d&auml;ldir.&nbsp;Kurslar -
amaly &yacute;erine baglylykda 4-8 hepde.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Aktiwle&#351;dirilen sink piritionyny&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&ouml;z&nbsp;<b>i&ccedil;ine
al&yacute;an ta&yacute;&yacute;arlyklar&nbsp;</b>, 2-3 a&yacute;a &ccedil;enli
kurslar &uuml;&ccedil;in aerozol, krem &#8203;&#8203;we &#351;ampun
g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;inde ulanyl&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Ulgamla&yacute;yn bejergi</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Orta we agyr
g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;ler &uuml;&ccedil;in g&ouml;rkezil&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Sitostatiki dermanlar&nbsp;(metotreksat)&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>-
bellemek we dolandyrmak laboratori&yacute;a parametrlerine yzygiderli
lukman&ccedil;ylyk g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;iligini we g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;iligi &ouml;z
i&ccedil;ine al&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Idearamaz t&auml;sirleri bolup
biler.&nbsp;Metotreksaty kabul etmek fol tur&#351;usyny kabul etmek bilen
birle&#351;dirilmelidir.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Retino kislotasyny&#328; ta&yacute;&yacute;arlyklary&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>agyr
g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;leri bejermek &uuml;&ccedil;in ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Deri
&ouml;&yacute;j&uuml;klerini&#328; tapawudyny&#328; t&auml;zelenmegi we
keratinizasi&yacute;a proseslerini kadala&#351;dyr&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Biologiki ta&yacute;&yacute;arlyklar&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>-
genetiki ta&yacute;dan d&ouml;redilen usullardan pe&yacute;dalanyp
d&ouml;redilen monoklonal antikorlary&#328;
ta&yacute;&yacute;arlyklary.&nbsp;Antikorlar psoriazy&#328; &ouml;smeginde
m&ouml;h&uuml;m rol o&yacute;na&yacute;an &ccedil;i&#351;me beloklaryny&#328;
belli bir antigenleri bilen baglany&#351;dyryl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>PUVA terapi&yacute;asy&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>(fotohimoterapi&yacute;a)
bejergini&#328; utga&#351;dyrylan usulydyr - retino kislotasyny&#328;
ta&yacute;&yacute;arlyklaryny&#328; we fototerapi&yacute;any&#328;
utga&#351;masy.&nbsp;Usuly&#328; t&auml;sirliligi, bejergini&#328;
d&uuml;z&uuml;m b&ouml;leklerini bilelikde ulanmak olary&#328; netijeliligini
&yacute;okarlandyr&yacute;ar, dozalary we &yacute;ygylygy azaltmaga
m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;ilik ber&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Bu bolsa &ouml;z gezeginde
zy&yacute;anly t&auml;sirleri azald&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Hirurgiki amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Psoriaz keselini bejermek
&uuml;&ccedil;in hirurgi&yacute;a zerur d&auml;l.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Durmu&#351;y&#328; hilini
dikeltmek we gowula&#351;dyrmak</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Durmu&#351;y&#328; hilini
kesgitlemek &uuml;&ccedil;in &yacute;&ouml;rite tereziler we anketalar
ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Akyl we fiziki komponentleri&#328; durmu&#351;
derejesini&#328; peselmegi bar.&nbsp;Durmu&#351; g&ouml;rkezijilerini&#328;
&uuml;&yacute;tgemegini&#328; derejesi n&auml;sagy&#328; &yacute;a&#351;yna,
keseli&#328; dowamlylygyna, agyrla&#351;ma &yacute;ygylygyna we
birle&#351;&yacute;&auml;n keselleri&#328; barlygyna baglydyr.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>M&uuml;mkin kyn&ccedil;ylyklar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Derini&#328; ikinji derejeli &yacute;okan&ccedil;lygy&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>-
&yacute;erli immuniteti&#328; bozulmagy bilen &#351;ikeslenen deri d&uuml;rli
bakteri&yacute;alar &uuml;&ccedil;in amatly k&ouml;pel&yacute;&auml;n
&yacute;ere &ouml;wr&uuml;l&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Bu &#351;ertleri&#328;
&ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni almak &uuml;&ccedil;in, &ccedil;i&#351;m&auml; gar&#351;y
melhemlere antibiotikler we antifungal komponentler gir&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>G&ouml;z&uuml;&#328; &ccedil;i&#351;me keselleri&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>:
kon&yacute;uktiwit, blefarit (gabaklary&#328; gyralaryny&#328;
&ccedil;i&#351;megi), uveit (horidi&#328;
&ccedil;i&#351;megi).&nbsp;K&auml;wagt bu toshba&yacute;azy&#328;
d&ouml;remegini&#328; ilkinji alamatydyr.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Psoriatik artrit&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>- bogun &ccedil;i&#351;mesi,
esasanam ba&#351;ga alamatlar bolmadyk &yacute;agda&yacute;ynda &yacute;a-da
keseli&#328; &ccedil;yl&#351;yrymlylygy bilen&nbsp;<b>toshba&yacute;azy&#328;&nbsp;</b>&yacute;&uuml;ze
&ccedil;ykmagy bolup biler.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Awtoimmun kesellerini&#328; &ouml;smegi&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>-
toshba&yacute;azly n&auml;saglar, s&uuml;&yacute;ji keselinden (gl&yacute;uten
&ccedil;ydamsyzlygy), Crohn keselinden has k&ouml;p ejir
&ccedil;ek&yacute;&auml;rler.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Psihoemosional sferany&#328; bozulmagy&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>- agyr
gyjyndyrma, estetiki we fiziki n&auml;sazlyklar bilen baglany&#351;ykly
o&#328;a&yacute;syzlyk, n&auml;sagy&#328; ne&yacute;rotizasi&yacute;asyna
seb&auml;p bol&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni aly&#351;
&ccedil;&auml;releri</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Psoriaz keselini&#328;
&ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni almak &uuml;&ccedil;in hi&ccedil; hili usul
&yacute;ok.&nbsp;&Uuml;&yacute;tge&yacute;&auml;n t&ouml;wekgel&ccedil;ilik
faktorlaryny&#328; d&uuml;zedilmegini&#328; keseli&#328; &ouml;smegine
t&auml;sir ed&yacute;&auml;ndigini &yacute;a-da &yacute;okdugyny kesgitlemek
m&uuml;mkin d&auml;l.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ccedil;aklama</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Psoriazy&#328; o&#328;at ugry
bardygyna garamazdan, bu &ouml;m&uuml;rlik remissi&yacute;a we agyrla&#351;ma
keseli.&nbsp;Se&yacute;rek &yacute;agda&yacute;larda toshba&yacute;az
bejerg&auml; jogap berme&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>G&ouml;zlegleri&#328;
netijesinde psoriazy&#328; &yacute;&uuml;rek-damar keseli, s&uuml;&yacute;ji
keseli, b&ouml;wrek we bogun kesellerini&#328; &yacute;okary
t&ouml;wekgel&ccedil;iligi bilen baglany&#351;yklydygy
g&ouml;rkezil&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Agyr, pes g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilik
edil&yacute;&auml;n psoriaz keseli bilen kesell&auml;nler, psoriaz keselinden
3-4 &yacute;yl &ouml;&#328; &ouml;l&yacute;&auml;rler.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Lukmandan ha&yacute;sy
soraglary bermeli?</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Alamatlary&#328; seb&auml;bi n&auml;me?</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Ha&yacute;sy g&ouml;zleg gerek?</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Bejergini&#328; ha&yacute;sy usullary bar, bu meni&#328;
&uuml;&ccedil;in dogry?</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Terapi&yacute;any&#328; ters t&auml;sirleri bolup bilermi?</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Alamatlar &yacute;ok bolarmy?</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Mende o&#328;a&yacute;syzlyklar bar.&nbsp;Bejergini n&auml;dip
birle&#351;dirmeli?</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Deri&#328;ize n&auml;dip ideg etmeli?</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Ulanylan
edebi&yacute;aty&#328; sanawy</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='line-height:normal'><span style='color:black'>&nbsp;</span></p>

